 DockerService Implementation\n\n**Source file:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` (221 lines)\n\n**Class: `DockerService`**\n\n| Method | Signature | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|---------|\n| `__init__` | `(verbose: bool = False)` | Constructor storing verbose flag |\n| `check_docker_available` | `() -> bool` | Pings Docker daemon, returns True/False |\n| `build_image` | `(dockerfile_path, context_path, image_name, tag=\"latest\", build_args=None) -> Dict[str, str]` | Builds Docker image, returns metadata (image_name, image_id, image_size, build_time) |\n| `get_image_info` | `(image_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]` | Gets local image metadata; raises ValueError if not found |\n| `_get_image_info` | `(image_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]` | Internal helper for image metadata retrieval |\n| `_format_size` | `(size_bytes: int) -> str` | Formats bytes to human-readable (B/KB/MB/GB) |\n| `push_image` | `(image_name, registry_url=None, username=None, password=None) -> Dict[str, str]` | Pushes image to registry, returns pushed_image and push_time |\n| `_docker_login_sdk` | `(registry_url, username, password) -> None` | Logs into Docker registry via SDK |\n| `_tag_image_sdk` | `(source_image, target_image) -> None` | Tags a local image with new name |\n| `remove_image` | `(image_name: str) -> bool` | Removes local image; returns True/False |\n\n**Consumers of DockerService:**\n- `BuildRuntime` (`build_runtime.py` lines 12, 81-83, 89) -- uses `check_docker_available()` and `build_image()` for local builds\n- `PublishRuntime` (`publish_runtime.py` lines 9, 83) -- uses `check_docker_available()`, `_docker_login_sdk()`, and `push_image()` for local image publishing\n\n**Test file:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py` (424 lines, 17 test classes covering all methods including edge cases)\n\n**Design doc:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/design.md` -- Full DockerService design with architecture diagrams, method signatures, error handling strategy, and test matrix.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28694ccf4ffeCUqHjv0q8ds1IT","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project","time":{"start":1775858561800,"end":1775858757084}}}}
